🧠 Design Notes (Important)
IBM MQ client is NOT fully async, so we wrap with async pattern
Avoid creating MQQueueManager per message in production → use pooling
Always handle:
MQRC_NO_MSG_AVAILABLE
MQRC_NOT_AUTHORIZED
MQRC_CONNECTION_BROKEN